Foxfingers gets a quick whiff of someone comming the other way. he 
dives out of the doorway as the missles impact. The concussion sends 
him sliding into the wall on the other side of the hallway. the door 
was destroyed so Foxfingers decided to use it. "Thanks for the key." 
he calls to bludgeon as he scampers into it. (I'll keep this 
interesting and let either Kinger or Logo post where the door leads. 
whomever posts first makes the call.)
